      <h2 class="h2">SWEP (Severe Weather Emergency Provision) is now active.</h2>
      <p>Extra emergency beds are available <u>tonight</u> for people sleeping rough in Cambridgeshire, due to severe weather.</p>
      <p>If you are sleeping rough and need a bed for the night, please present yourself to <a href="https://streetsupport.net/find-help/organisation/?organisation=jimmy39s-cambridge">Jimmy's</a> between 11am and 5pm, or call 01223 576085.</p>
      <p>You can find more information about our severe weather emergency provision <a href="https://streetsupport.net/find-help/accommodation/listing/details/?id=5ddb994d18965a0eac46fb40">here</a>.</p>
