      <h2 class="h1 best-practice__header">If your see someone sleeping rough you can</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Contact the Cambridge Street Outreach team on <a href="tel:01223366292">01223 366292</a>, Monday to Friday, 9am to 5pm.</li>
        <li>Use the <a href="https://www.streetlink.org.uk/">Streetlink app</a> anytime or call Streetlink on <a href="tel:03005000914">0300 500 0914</a> (bearing in mind that phone lines can get busy).</li>
        <li>Refer the person to <a href="https://streetsupport.net/find-help/organisation/?organisation=jimmy39s-cambridge">Jimmy's</a> at 1 East Road, Cambridge, CB1 1BD or call <a href="tel:01223576085">01223 576085</a> 24 hours a day, 7 days a week. Alternatively, you can contact <a href="https://jimmyscambridge.org.uk/contact">Jimmy's on-line</a>.</li>
        <p><strong>If the person is under 18 - if you think they are in immediate danger - if they need urgent care - or you feel they are unwell, please call 999.</strong></p>
      </ul>
